 public double evaluate(double x,double epsilon,int maxIterations) throws MathException{
 double p0=1.0;
-double p1=getA(0,x);
+ double p1=getA(0,x);
 double q0=0.0;
 double q1=1.0;
 double c=p1/q1;
 int n=0;
 double relativeError=Double.MAX_VALUE;
 while(n<maxIterations&&relativeError>epsilon){
 ++n;
 double a=getA(n,x);
 double b=getB(n,x);
 double p2=a*p1+b*p0;
 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;
  final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 infinite=true;
 for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
 lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
 scaleFactor*=scale;
 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {
 if(b!=0){
 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;
 }

 scaleFactor*=scale;

 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;

 double p0=1.0;
 double p1=getA(0,x);
 double q0=0.0;
 double q1=1.0;
 double c=p1/q1;
 int n=0;
 double relativeError=Double.MAX_VALUE;
 while(n<maxIterations&&relativeError>epsilon){
 ++n;
 double a=getA(n,x);
 double b=getB(n,x);
 double p2=a*p1+b*p0;
 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;
  final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 infinite=true;
-for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
+for(int i=0;c<maxPower;i++){
 lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
 scaleFactor*=scale;
 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {
 if(b!=0){
 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;
 }

 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {
 if(b!=0){
 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);

 p0=p1;

 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;

 public double evaluate(double x,double epsilon,int maxIterations) throws MathException{
 double p0=1.0;
 double p1=getA(0,x);
 double q0=0.0;
 double q1=1.0;
 double c=p1/q1;
 int n=0;
 double relativeError=Double.MAX_VALUE;
 while(n<maxIterations&&relativeError>epsilon){
 ++n;
 double a=getA(n,x);
 double b=getB(n,x);
 double p2=a*p1+b*p0;
 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;
  final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 infinite=true;
 for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
 lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
 scaleFactor*=scale;
 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {
 if(b!=0){
 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
-throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
+throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",relativeError,x);
 }
 return c;

 if(b!=0){
 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
-p0=p1;
+p0=q1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;
 }

 double a=getA(n,x);
 double b=getB(n,x);
 double p2=a*p1+b*p0;
 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;
  final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 infinite=true;
 for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
 lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
 scaleFactor*=scale;
 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){

 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);

 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;

------------Candidate---------------
 public double evaluate(double x,double epsilon,int maxIterations) throws MathException{
 double p0=1.0;
 double p1=getA(0,x);
 double q0=0.0;
 double q1=1.0;
 double c=p1/q1;
 int n=0;
 double relativeError=Double.MAX_VALUE;
 while(n<maxIterations&&relativeError>epsilon){
 ++n;
 double a=getA(n,x);
 double b=getB(n,x);
 double p2=a*p1+b*p0;
 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;
  final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 infinite=true;
 for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
 lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
 scaleFactor*=scale;
 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {
 if(b!=0){
 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
-relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
+relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-p1);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;
 }

 public double evaluate(double x,double epsilon,int maxIterations) throws MathException{
 double p0=1.0;
 double p1=getA(0,x);
 double q0=0.0;
 double q1=1.0;
 double c=p1/q1;
 int n=0;
 double relativeError=Double.MAX_VALUE;
 while(n<maxIterations&&relativeError>epsilon){
 ++n;
 double a=getA(n,x);
 double b=getB(n,x);
 double p2=a*p1+b*p0;
 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;
  final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 infinite=true;
 for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
 lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
 scaleFactor*=scale;
 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {
 if(b!=0){
 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
-p1=p2;
+p1=2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;
 }

 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){

 ++n;

 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;
  final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 infinite=true;
 for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
 lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
 scaleFactor*=scale;
 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {
 if(b!=0){
 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }

 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){

 p0=p1;

 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;

 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);

 q0=q1;

 }

 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);

 public double evaluate(double x,double epsilon,int maxIterations) throws MathException{
 double p0=1.0;
 double p1=getA(0,x);
 double q0=0.0;
 double q1=1.0;
 double c=p1/q1;
 int n=0;
 double relativeError=Double.MAX_VALUE;
 while(n<maxIterations&&relativeError>epsilon){
 ++n;
 double a=getA(n,x);
 double b=getB(n,x);
 double p2=a*p1+b*p0;
 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;
  final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 infinite=true;
 for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
 lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
 scaleFactor*=scale;
 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {
 if(b!=0){
 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
-p1=p2;
+p1=50;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;
 }

 public double evaluate(double x,double epsilon,int maxIterations) throws MathException{
 double p0=1.0;

 double q0=0.0;
 double q1=1.0;

 double relativeError=Double.MAX_VALUE;
 while(n<maxIterations&&relativeError>epsilon){
 ++n;

 double b=getB(n,x);

 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;
  final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 infinite=true;
 for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
 lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
 scaleFactor*=scale;
 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {

 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }

 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);

 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);

 scaleFactor*=scale;

 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {
 if(b!=0){

 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }

 }
 }
 }

 }

 ++n;

 double b=getB(n,x);
 double p2=a*p1+b*p0;
 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;
  final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 infinite=true;
 for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
 lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
 scaleFactor*=scale;
 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {

 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }

 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;

 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }

 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);

 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;
 }

 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;

 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);

 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;

 double p0=1.0;
 double p1=getA(0,x);
 double q0=0.0;
 double q1=1.0;
 double c=p1/q1;
 int n=0;
 double relativeError=Double.MAX_VALUE;
 while(n<maxIterations&&relativeError>epsilon){
 ++n;
 double a=getA(n,x);
 double b=getB(n,x);
 double p2=a*p1+b*p0;
 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;
  final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 infinite=true;
 for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
 lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
 scaleFactor*=scale;
 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {
 if(b!=0){
 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
+synchronized(this){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
+}
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;
 }

 scaleFactor*=scale;

 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);

 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;

 if(!infinite){

 }

+double p1=getA(0,Math.max(0,x));
 double q0=0.0;
 double q1=1.0;
 double c=p1/q1;
 int n=0;
 double relativeError=Double.MAX_VALUE;
 while(n<maxIterations&&relativeError>epsilon){
 ++n;
 double a=getA(n,x);
 double b=getB(n,x);
 double p2=a*p1+b*p0;
 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;
  final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 infinite=true;
 for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
 lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
 scaleFactor*=scale;
 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {
 if(b!=0){
 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;
 }

 ++n;

 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;

 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);

 infinite=true;

 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;

 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
-p1=p2;
+p1=p1+p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;
 }

 public double evaluate(double x,double epsilon,int maxIterations) throws MathException{
 double p0=1.0;
 double p1=getA(0,x);
 double q0=0.0;
 double q1=1.0;
 double c=p1/q1;
 int n=0;
 double relativeError=Double.MAX_VALUE;
 while(n<maxIterations&&relativeError>epsilon){
 ++n;
 double a=getA(n,x);
 double b=getB(n,x);
 double p2=a*p1+b*p0;
 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;
  final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 infinite=true;
 for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
 lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
 scaleFactor*=scale;
 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {
 if(b!=0){
 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
+if(r==p2/q2){
+return b;
+}
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;
 }

 q1=q2;

 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);

 ++n;

 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;
  final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 infinite=true;
 for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
 lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
 scaleFactor*=scale;
 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {
 if(b!=0){
 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }

 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);

 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);

 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;

 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }

 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);

 return c;

 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;
 }

 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);

 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {
 if(b!=0){
-p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
+p2=x+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;
 }

 double p0=1.0;
 double p1=getA(0,x);
 double q0=0.0;
 double q1=1.0;
 double c=p1/q1;

 while(n<maxIterations&&relativeError>epsilon){
 ++n;

 double b=getB(n,x);
 double p2=a*p1+b*p0;
 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;

 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }

 }

 public double evaluate(double x,double epsilon,int maxIterations) throws MathException{
 double p0=1.0;
 double p1=getA(0,x);
 double q0=0.0;
 double q1=1.0;
 double c=p1/q1;
 int n=0;
 double relativeError=Double.MAX_VALUE;
 while(n<maxIterations&&relativeError>epsilon){
 ++n;
 double a=getA(n,x);
 double b=getB(n,x);
 double p2=a*p1+b*p0;
 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;
  final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 infinite=true;
 for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
+assert (p0!=0):"Receive a size tratment";
 lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
 scaleFactor*=scale;
 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {
 if(b!=0){
 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;

 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;
 }

------------Candidate---------------
 public double evaluate(double x,double epsilon,int maxIterations) throws MathException{
 double p0=1.0;
 double p1=getA(0,x);
 double q0=0.0;
 double q1=1.0;
 double c=p1/q1;
 int n=0;
 double relativeError=Double.MAX_VALUE;
 while(n<maxIterations&&relativeError>epsilon){
 ++n;
 double a=getA(n,x);
 double b=getB(n,x);
 double p2=a*p1+b*p0;
 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
+if(b<=0){
+b=1;
+}
 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;
  final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 infinite=true;
 for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
 lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
 scaleFactor*=scale;
 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {
 if(b!=0){
 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;
 }

 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;

------------Candidate---------------
 public double evaluate(double x,double epsilon,int maxIterations) throws MathException{
 double p0=1.0;
 double p1=getA(0,x);
 double q0=0.0;
 double q1=1.0;
 double c=p1/q1;
 int n=0;
 double relativeError=Double.MAX_VALUE;
 while(n<maxIterations&&relativeError>epsilon){
 ++n;
 double a=getA(n,x);
 double b=getB(n,x);
-double p2=a*p1+b*p0;
+double p2=(double)a*p1+(double)b*p0;
 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;
  final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 infinite=true;
 for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
 lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
 scaleFactor*=scale;
 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {
 if(b!=0){
 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;
 }

 public double evaluate(double x,double epsilon,int maxIterations) throws MathException{
 double p0=1.0;
 double p1=getA(0,x);
 double q0=0.0;
 double q1=1.0;
 double c=p1/q1;
 int n=0;
 double relativeError=Double.MAX_VALUE;
 while(n<maxIterations&&relativeError>epsilon){
 ++n;
 double a=getA(n,x);
 double b=getB(n,x);
 double p2=a*p1+b*p0;
 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;
  final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 infinite=true;
 for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
 lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
 scaleFactor*=scale;
 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {
 if(b!=0){
 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
-relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
+relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0)*x;
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;
 }

 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }

 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);

+relativeError=-1;
+relativeError++;

 p0=p1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }

 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);

 public double evaluate(double x,double epsilon,int maxIterations) throws MathException{
 double p0=1.0;

 double q1=1.0;
 double c=p1/q1;
 int n=0;
 double relativeError=Double.MAX_VALUE;
 while(n<maxIterations&&relativeError>epsilon){
+if(p0<0){
+return 0;
+}
+if(p0>=q1){
+return q1-1;
+}
 ++n;
 double a=getA(n,x);
 double b=getB(n,x);
 double p2=a*p1+b*p0;
 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
  final int maxPower=5;
  final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 infinite=true;
 for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
 lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
 scaleFactor*=scale;
 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {
 if(b!=0){
 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;

 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }

 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;

 public double evaluate(double x,double epsilon,int maxIterations) throws MathException{
 double p0=1.0;
 double p1=getA(0,x);
 double q0=0.0;
 double q1=1.0;
 double c=p1/q1;
 int n=0;
 double relativeError=Double.MAX_VALUE;
 while(n<maxIterations&&relativeError>epsilon){
 ++n;
 double a=getA(n,x);
 double b=getB(n,x);
 double p2=a*p1+b*p0;
 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
 if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
 double scaleFactor=1.0;
 double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
+infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
  final int maxPower=5;
  final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
 if(scale<=0){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 infinite=true;
 for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
 lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
 scaleFactor*=scale;
 if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
 p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
 q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
 }else {
 if(b!=0){
 p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
 q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
 }
 }
 infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
 if(!infinite){
 break;
 }
 }
 }
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;

 int n=0;
 double relativeError=Double.MAX_VALUE;
 while(n<maxIterations&&relativeError>epsilon){
 ++n;
 double a=getA(n,x);
 double b=getB(n,x);
 double p2=a*p1+b*p0;
 double q2=a*q1+b*q0;
 boolean infinite=false;
-if(Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2)){
-double scaleFactor=1.0;
-double lastScaleFactor=1.0;
- final int maxPower=5;
- final double scale=Math.max(a,b);
-if(scale<=0){
-throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
-}
-infinite=true;
-for(int i=0;i<maxPower;i++){
-lastScaleFactor=scaleFactor;
-scaleFactor*=scale;
-if(a!=0.0&&a>b){
-p2=p1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*p0);
-q2=q1/lastScaleFactor+(b/scaleFactor*q0);
-}else {
-if(b!=0){
-p2=(a/scaleFactor*p1)+p0/lastScaleFactor;
-q2=(a/scaleFactor*q1)+q0/lastScaleFactor;
-}
-}
-infinite=Double.isInfinite(p2)||Double.isInfinite(q2);
-if(!infinite){
-break;
-}
-}
-}
 if(infinite){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction convergents diverged to +/- infinity for value {0}",x);
 }
 double r=p2/q2;
 if(Double.isNaN(r)){
 throw new ConvergenceException("Continued fraction diverged to NaN for value {0}",x);
 }
 relativeError=Math.abs(r/c-1.0);
 c=p2/q2;
 p0=p1;
 p1=p2;
 q0=q1;
 q1=q2;
 }
 if(n>=maxIterations){
 throw new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIterations,"Continued fraction convergents failed to converge for value {0}",x);
 }
 return c;
 }
